{"tid":1841082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動po] 封印高鐵  封印高鐵  封印高鐵","createTime":"2020-01-25T06:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:27:29.000Z","uid":24390,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a7bf4ffd9da969bac2a49eba9ec571d9e8dcd9","tid":1841082,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:38:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>特殊行動  <span style=\"color: red;\">封印</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">高鐵</span>大行動 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvhZUFb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvhZUFb.jpg&h=6dd89f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VVCK5MW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVVCK5MW.jpg&h=6f687007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目標 : 只有一個 封印高鐵 !! <br />\n時間 : 初一至初四 兩點 !<br />\n地點 : 西九高鐵站 <br />\n行動 :<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M3diy2M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM3diy2M.png&h=dc1dd47d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係A點同B點集合之後行向高鐵站<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">高鐵不封 ！ </span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\"> 港人必亡 ！</span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">高鐵不封 ！ </span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">肺炎失控 ！</span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">政府不封 !  </span>  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">港人必亡 !</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">港人自救 ！ </span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">不封不散 ！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: red;\">香港封關！ </span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"> 肺炎不散 ！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n高鐵如果一日<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲運作 </span></span><br />\n就代表緊每日都有成千上萬個<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">武漢人同中國肺炎人可以入境播毒</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無能政府仲依然要<span style=\"color: red;\">政治大於人命</span>  連<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">拒絕武漢人入境</span>都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以一定要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己香港自己救</span></span></strong>! <br />\n<br />\n我地唔須要呢個<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">害我地於死地既高鐵</span></span></strong> !<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中左肺炎無藥醫 !</span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">肺炎傳播就會死 !</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁你願意行出黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護自己條命嗎?</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n唔好<span style=\"color: red;\">本未倒置</span>話去左高鐵就會病死 <br />\n拎自己條命較飛<br />\n你唔幫手封關不斷俾人輸入病原個體先係拎緊自己條命較飛呀!<br />\n佢入左香港D毒咪散播緊咯<br />\n 你以為靠你一個口罩就頂得住?</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n到時你既<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不作為</span></span></strong>就係好似<span style=\"color: red;\">上一代</span>咁害死緊下一代同呢家呢代既人</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最後一推 推唔起 香港人自己受</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#2為投稿"},{"pid":"ef3d6e3671509d2190a41b756a2f2e042ed43d9d","tid":1841082,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"希望大家依家開始多啲推行動po"},{"pid":"c84d6c721d1c68de98cf037bbdfff86989db6c97","tid":1841082,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:40:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">CLS 唔怪知得又豬瘟又肺炎啦屌</span></strong><br />\n<strong>中國科學院武漢病毒研究所</strong>牽頭的科研團隊近日確定<br />\n一年多前曾在廣東導致大量豬死亡的流行性腹瀉罪魁禍首是一種源自蝙蝠的新型冠狀病毒<br />\n<br />\n研究人員通過對病豬腸道樣本的高通量測序，病毒分離和感染實驗証實<br />\n該病源是一種來源於菊頭蝠的新型冠狀病毒，並將其命名為豬急性腹瀉綜合徵冠狀病毒，簡稱SADS冠狀病毒<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>專家介紹，SADS冠狀病毒雖然<ins>目前</ins>不會感染人，但是其<ins>與2003年爆發的SARS病毒有諸多相似性</ins><br />\n其溯源研究也證實了蝙蝠㩦帶的某些冠狀病毒可跨種傳播至家畜，並造成嚴重疾病</strong></span><br />\n針對蝙蝠持續開展冠狀病毒的監測，對於防控新發傳染病、保障畜牧業生產安全具有重要意義<br />\n<br />\n現在病毒已經分離出來了，我們也製備了相應的抗體啊疫苖很快的就能夠針對這些病毒的蔓延<br />\n<br />\n[24小时]国内焦点 科学家发现新型冠状病毒<br />\n来源：央视网<strong>2018年</strong>04月05日 23:32<br />\n<a href=\"http://tv.cctv.com/2018/04/05/VIDE9RUDynaxH6cGkEAZah6k180405.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftv.cctv.com%2F2018%2F04%2F05%2FVIDE9RUDynaxH6cGkEAZah6k180405.shtml&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2Fa%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=53894f24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tv.cctv.com/2018/04/05/VIDE9RUDynaxH6cGkEAZah6k180405.shtml</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/1yQXO9S.jpg\" /><br />\n1.<strong> 2018年</strong>中國首個P4實驗室於武漢啟用，「P4 實驗室研究的傳染性微生物一般都是<ins>無預防和治療方法</ins>的病毒」。<br />\n<br />\n2. 管軼表示病毒「源頭被銷毀得乾乾淨淨，這裏似乎不歡迎專家」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 中國喺初期一直拒絕公開病毒基因圖譜。<br />\n<br />\n4. 專家認為病毒由蝙蝠傳畀蛇，「但目前關於新病毒如何能同時適應冷血動物和溫血動物宿主，還是個謎。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">SADS+SARS+MERS</span></strong>"},{"pid":"030d257594b35927522f66d8f444d1d984fbe4b5","tid":1841082,"uid":114946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:25:3